            <abstract xml:lang="en">
              <p>We introduce VoxPopuli, a large-scale multilingual corpus providing 400K hours of unlabeled speech data in 23 languages. It is the largest open data to date for unsupervised representation learning as well as semisupervised learning. VoxPopuli also contains 1.8K hours of transcribed speeches in 15 languages and their aligned oral interpretations into 15 target languages totaling 17.3K hours. We provide speech recognition (ASR) baselines and validate the versatility of VoxPopuli unlabeled data in semisupervised ASR and speech-to-text translation under challenging out-of-domain settings. The corpus is available at https://github. com/facebookresearch/voxpopuli.</p>
